---
title: Orange-Glazed Meatballs with Crispy Broccolini and Rice
description: Broccolini, which is a cross between broccoli and Chinese kale, has a subtle peppery flavor, slightly crunchy texture, and slender stalks. The pop of green color in this dish looks stunning alongside the meatballs, a hearty scoop of rice, and a drizzle of citrusy glaze.
